{"tid":992060,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"鹿兒島機場 > 熊本 / 霧島 大浪池 點揀好","createTime":"2019-01-23T01:19:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T10:35:31.000Z","uid":5097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"40cc03df14cee23e541bfa5655b1c7ffbc894bbf","tid":992060,"uid":5097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T01:19:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的 黎緊會去鹿兒島 但落機之後 有選擇困難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直接去熊本 等第二日上阿蘇好<br />\n定去霧島 等第二日去大浪池<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大浪池回程嘅車都好疏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 8點半去到 1點先有車返 有冇巴打 試過狗衝上埋韓國岳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就咁大浪池好似有排等咁<br />\n<br />\n點揀好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208fc46ea062f2d1f80cac9a20e7cea50c12d836","tid":992060,"uid":55851,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T01:24:09.000Z","msg":"鹿兒島機場-&gt;鹿兒島中央JR-&gt;新大阪JR-&gt;飛田新地"},{"pid":"678b23543def1fb79bcb6f77c8647fe58f12bbe1","tid":992060,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T04:14:31.000Z","msg":"霧島搭巴士=on9<br />\n<br />\n直上熊本好過"},{"pid":"c630ba0c874167ea17e3c98674cc999b453769b4","tid":992060,"uid":31991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T04:19:15.000Z","msg":"你想浸溫泉可以去霧島瞓返晚<br />\n不過要搭巴士真係好on9"},{"pid":"caf6159399c3d33abf328839842118b6f20a5db4","tid":992060,"uid":181348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T04:27:10.000Z","msg":"上上年去左霧島，行埋大浪池同韓國岳<br />\n<br />\n巴打如果鍾意睇自然風景行山既就去啦<br />\n<br />\n阿蘇我都有去，但我覺得霧島靚好多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/23/122650_1a0e2fad2e131924d1b6f7300f61c2ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=